 end="2:38.054">na ka</span></text><text for="L38"><span begin="2:38.264" end="2:38.513">「sa</span><span begin="2:38.513" end="2:38.648">yo</span><span begin="2:38.648" end="2:38.764">u</span><span begin="2:38.764" end="2:38.945">na</span><span begin="2:38.945" end="2:39.145">ra」</span><span begin="2:39.145" end="2:39.335">to</span> <span begin="2:39.335" end="2:39.500">te</span><span begin="2:39.500" end="2:39.720">wo</span><span begin="2:39.720" end="2:39.914">fu</span><span begin="2:39.914" end="2:40.935">ru</span></text><text for="L39"><span begin="2:41.069" end="2:41.661">e i</span><span begin="2:41.661" end="2:42.258">e n</span><span begin="2:42.258" end="2:45.562">ni</span></text></transliteration></transliterations></iTunesMetadata></metadata></head><body dur="2:45.562"><div begin="12.677" end="2:45.562"><p begin="12.677" end="18.718" itunes:key="L1" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="12.677" end="13.242">鉛</span><span begin="13.242" end="14.005">筆</span><span begin="14.005" end="14.231">で</span><span begin="14.231" end="14.605">ノ</span><span begin="14.605" end="14.999">ー</span><span begin="14.999" end="15.181">ト</span><span begin="15.181" end="15.373">に</span><span begin="15.373" end="15.959">落</span><span begin="15.959" end="16.337">書</span><span begin="16.337" end="16.468">き</span><span begin="16.468" end="17.136">し</span><span begin="17.136" end="17.374">て</span><span begin="17.374" end="17.980">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">握着铅笔在本子上乱涂乱画</span></p><p begin="18.718" end="24.387" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="18.718" end="18.916">あ</span><span begin="18.916" end="19.094">な</span><span begin="19.094" end="19.497">た</span><span begin="19.497" end="19.707">の</span><span begin="19.707" end="20.249">名</span><span begin="20.249" end="20.981">前</span><span begin="20.981" end="21.426">を</span><span begin="21.426" end="22.008">何</span><span begin="22.008" end="22.209">度</span><span begin="22.209" end="22.394">も</span><span begin="22.394" end="22.551">書</span><span begin="22.551" end="22.782">き</span><span begin="22.782" end="23.012">込</span><span begin="23.012" end="23.198">ん</span><span begin="23.198" end="23.362">で</span><span begin="23.362" end="23.496">消</span><span begin="23.496" end="24.190">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一遍遍地写满你的名字又擦掉</span></p><p begin="25.118" end="31.108" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="25.118" end="25.327">ノ</span><span begin="25.327" end="25.677">ー</span><span begin="25.677" end="25.876">ト</span><span begin="25.876" end="26.274">と</span><span begin="26.274" end="26.629">る</span><span begin="26.629" end="27.429">君</span><span begin="27.429" end="27.630">の</span><span begin="27.630" end="28.030">横</span><span begin="28.030" end="28.762">顔</span> <span begin="28.762" end="29.032">つ</span><span begin="29.032" end="29.565">い</span><span begin="29.565" end="29.789">見</span><span begin="29.789" end="30.410">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">忍不住偷看你认真记笔记的侧脸</span></p><p begin="31.108" end="36.640" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="31.108" end="31.283">な</span><span begin="31.283" end="31.528">ぜ</span><span begin="31.528" end="31.722">か</span><span begin="31.722" end="32.216">首</span><span begin="32.216" end="32.898">筋</span><span begin="32.898" end="33.441">が</span><span begin="33.690" end="34.054">熱</span><span begin="34.054" end="34.278">く</span><span begin="34.278" end="34.449">て</span> <span begin="34.449" end="34.584">気</span><span begin="34.584" end="35.029">づ</span><span begin="35.029" end="35.230">か</span><span begin="35.230" end="35.616">れ</span><span begin="35.616" end="35.819">た</span><span begin="35.819" end="36.019">か</span><span begin="36.019" end="36.640">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">脖子莫名发烫 有没有被你发现呢</span></p><p begin="36.939" end="39.130" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.939" end="37.138">き</span><span begin="37.138" end="37.230">っ</span><span begin="37.274" end="37.689">と</span> <span begin="37.689" end="37.927">好</span><span begin="37.927" end="38.163">き</span><span begin="38.163" end="38.350">に</span><span begin="38.350" end="38.460">な</span><span begin="38.460" end="38.520">っ</span><span begin="38.520" end="38.750">ちゃ</span><span begin="38.750" end="38.922">っ</span><span begin="38.922" end="39.130">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一定是喜欢上你了</span></p><p begin="39.130" end="43.216" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="39.130" end="39.717">胸</span><span begin="39.717" end="40.100">が</span><span begin="40.100" end="40.886">痛</span><span begin="40.886" end="41.619">い</span><span begin="41.619" end="42.250">く</span><span begin="42.250" end="42.838">ら</span><span begin="42.838" end="43.216">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">喜欢到胸口都隐隐作痛</span></p><p begin="43.621" end="46.898" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="43.621" end="43.817">名</span><span begin="43.817" end="44.146">前</span><span begin="44.146" end="44.411">呼</span><span begin="44.411" end="44.596">ば</span><span begin="44.596" end="44.802">れ</span><span begin="44.802" end="44.973">る</span><span begin="44.973" end="45.370">た</span><span begin="45.370" end="45.740">び</span><span begin="45.740" end="45.929">に</span> <span begin="45.929" end="46.137">揺</span><span begin="46.137" end="46.534">れ</span><span begin="46.534" end="46.802">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每次被你叫到名字 心都会动摇</span></p><p begin="46.898" end="49.391" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="46.898" end="47.284">平</span><span begin="47.284" end="47.514">気</span><span begin="47.514" end="47.707">な</span><span begin="47.707" end="47.908">ふ</span><span begin="47.908" end="48.274">り</span> <span begin="48.274" end="48.451">で</span><span begin="48.451" end="48.883">き</span><span begin="48.883" end="49.083">な</span><span begin="49.083" end="49.391">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">无法装作若无其事的样子</span></p><p begin="49.391" end="51.398" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="49.391" end="49.611">ず</span><span begin="49.611" end="49.830">っ</span><span begin="49.830" end="50.206">と</span> <span begin="50.206" end="50.622">隠</span><span begin="50.622" end="50.806">し</span><span begin="50.806" end="51.007">て</span><span begin="51.007" end="51.296">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一直悄悄藏着的</span></p><p begin="51.398" end="55.320" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="51.398" end="51.575">ポ</span><span begin="51.575" end="51.776">ケ</span><span begin="51.776" end="51.977">ッ</span><span begin="51.977" end="52.193">ト</span><span begin="52.193" end="52.357">の</span><span begin="52.357" end="52.976">中</span><span begin="52.976" end="53.206">の</span><span begin="53.206" end="54.088">「好</span><span begin="54.088" end="54.728">き」</span><span begin="54.728" end="55.320">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">口袋里那句“喜欢你”</span></p><p begin="55.448" end="58.580" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="55.448" end="56.077">君</span><span begin="56.077" end="56.251">に</span><span begin="56.251" end="56.843">届</span><span begin="56.843" end="57.048">け</span><span begin="57.048" end="57.250">た</span><span begin="57.250" end="57.465">い</span><span begin="57.465" end="57.639">ん</span><span begin="57.639" end="58.281">だ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真的好想传达给你</span></p><p begin="58.580" end="1:01.477" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="58.580" end="58.813">「や</span><span begin="58.813" end="59.008">っ</span><span begin="59.008" end="59.212">ぱ</span><span begin="59.212" end="59.384">り</span><span begin="59.384" end="59.611">や</span><span begin="59.611" end="59.790">め</span><span begin="59.790" end="59.980">と</span><span begin="59.980" end="1:00.165">く」</span><span begin="1:00.165" end="1:01.160">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“果然还是算了吧”</span></p><p begin="1:01.477" end="1:05.506" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:01.477" end="1:02.336">呟</span><span begin="1:02.336" end="1:02.542">い</span><span begin="1:02.542" end="1:05.506">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">小声嘟囔着</span></p><p begin="1:08.769" end="1:14.786" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:08.769" end="1:09.350">思</span><span begin="1:09.350" end="1:09.478">わ</span><span begin="1:09.478" end="1:10.047">ず</span><span begin="1:10.047" end="1:10.596">近</span><span begin="1:10.596" end="1:11.037">づ</span><span begin="1:11.037" end="1:11.266">き</span> <span begin="1:11.266" end="1:11.666">何</span><span begin="1:11.666" end="1:12.061">か</span><span begin="1:12.061" end="1:12.442">言</span><span begin="1:12.442" end="1:12.650">い</span><span begin="1:12.650" end="1:13.228">た</span><span begin="1:13.228" end="1:13.425">く</span><span begin="1:13.425" end="1:14.015">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">忍不住地靠近你 想要说点什么</span></p><p begin="1:14.786" end="1:20.400" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:14.786" end="1:14.993">た</span><span begin="1:14.993" end="1:15.161">だ</span><span begin="1:15.161" end="1:15.361">や</span><span begin="1:15.361" end="1:15.560">っ</span><span begin="1:15.560" end="1:15.761">と</span><span begin="1:15.761" end="1:16.132">の</span><span begin="1:16.132" end="1:16.536">こ</span><span begin="1:16.536" end="1:17.521">と</span><span begin="1:17.521" end="1:17.714">で</span><span begin="1:17.714" end="1:18.060">言</span><span begin="1:18.060" end="1:18.300">え</span><span begin="1:18.300" end="1:18.507">た</span><span begin="1:18.507" end="1:18.688">「ま</span><span begin="1:18.688" end="1:18.833">た</span><span begin="1:18.833" end="1:19.266">明</span><span begin="1:19.266" end="1:19.472">日」</span><span begin="1:19.472" end="1:19.649">だ</span><span begin="1:19.649" end="1:20.400">け</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">好不容易开口 却只挤出一句“明天见”</span></p><p begin="1:21.138" end="1:26.740" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:21.138" end="1:21.781">君</span><span begin="1:21.781" end="1:21.980">と</span><span begin="1:21.980" end="1:22.732">歩</span><span begin="1:22.732" end="1:23.140">い</span><span begin="1:23.140" end="1:23.437">て</span><span begin="1:23.437" end="1:23.750">い</span><span begin="1:23.750" end="1:23.954">る</span><span begin="1:23.954" end="1:24.122">だ</span><span begin="1:24.122" end="1:24.531">け</span><span begin="1:24.531" end="1:24.806">で</span><span begin="1:24.806" end="1:25.779">幸</span><span begin="1:25.779" end="1:26.740">せ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">仅仅是和你一起走着就觉得好幸福</span></p><p begin="1:27.238" end="1:29.808" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:27.238" end="1:27.647">「友</span><span begin="1:27.647" end="1:27.788">だ</span><span begin="1:27.788" end="1:28.212">ち</span><span begin="1:28.212" end="1:28.428">だ</span><span begin="1:28.428" end="1:28.634">よ</span><span begin="1:28.634" end="1:28.836">な」</span><span begin="1:28.836" end="1:29.005">っ</span><span begin="1:29.005" end="1:29.500">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想着“我们只是朋友啊”</span></p><p begin="1:29.808" end="1:32.826" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.808" end="1:30.181">笑</span><span begin="1:30.181" end="1:30.374">う</span><span begin="1:30.374" end="1:31.133">私</span><span begin="1:31.133" end="1:31.296">が</span><span begin="1:31.296" end="1:31.746">き</span><span begin="1:31.746" end="1:32.132">ら</span><span begin="1:32.132" end="1:32.826">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">讨厌这样强装笑颜的自己</span></p><p begin="1:33.059" end="1:35.228" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:33.059" end="1:33.268">き</span><span begin="1:33.268" end="1:33.477">っ</span><span begin="1:33.477" end="1:33.774">と</span> <span begin="1:33.774" end="1:34.001">好</span><span begin="1:34.001" end="1:34.270">き</span><span begin="1:34.270" end="1:34.397">が</span><span begin="1:34.397" end="1:34.647">あ</span><span begin="1:34.647" end="1:34.853">ふ</span><span begin="1:34.853" end="1:35.031">れ</span><span begin="1:35.031" end="1:35.228">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">对你的喜欢 快来溢出来了</span></p><p begin="1:35.228" end="1:39.210" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:35.228" end="1:35.810">言</span><span begin="1:35.810" end="1:36.200">葉</span><span begin="1:36.200" end="1:36.604">に</span><span begin="1:36.604" end="1:36.973">で</span><span begin="1:36.973" end="1:37.382">き</span><span begin="1:37.382" end="1:37.771">な</span><span begin="1:37.771" end="1:38.356">く</span><span begin="1:38.356" end="1:39.210">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可我却无法用言语表达</span></p><p begin="1:39.710" end="1:42.986" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:39.710" end="1:40.100">君</span><span begin="1:40.100" end="1:40.492">に</span><span begin="1:40.492" end="1:40.667">こ</span><span begin="1:40.667" end="1:40.893">の</span><span begin="1:40.893" end="1:41.256">想</span><span begin="1:41.256" end="1:41.431">い</span><span begin="1:41.431" end="1:42.034">伝</span><span begin="1:42.034" end="1:42.189">え</span><span begin="1:42.189" end="1:42.644">た</span><span begin="1:42.644" end="1:42.850">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">怀着想说出口的这份心情</span></p><p begin="1:42.986" end="1:45.468" itunes:key="L22" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="1:42.986" end="1:43.401">君</span><span begin="1:43.401" end="1:43.581">を</span><span begin="1:43.581" end="1:43.909">離</span><span begin="1:43.909" end="1:44.399">し</span><span begin="1:44.399" end="1:44.589">た</span><span begin="1:44.589" end="1:44.992">く</span><span begin="1:44.992" end="1:45.170">な</span><span begin="1:45.170" end="1:45.468">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">却害怕就此失去你</span></p><p begin="1:45.468" end="1:47.406" itunes:key="L23" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:45.468" end="1:45.713">ず</span><span begin="1:45.713" end="1:45.957">っ</span><span begin="1:45.957" end="1:46.263">と</span> <span begin="1:46.263" end="1:46.725">探</span><span begin="1:46.725" end="1:46.920">し</span><span begin="1:46.920" end="1:47.105">て</span><span begin="1:47.105" end="1:47.406">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我一直在寻找着</span></p><p begin="1:47.406" end="1:51.328" itunes:key="L24" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:47.406" end="1:48.109">伝</span><span begin="1:48.109" end="1:48.293">え</span><span begin="1:48.293" end="1:48.476">る</span><span begin="1:48.476" end="1:48.683">た</span><span begin="1:48.683" end="1:49.082">め</span><span begin="1:49.082" end="1:49.403">の</span><span begin="1:49.403" end="1:50.189">勇</span><span begin="1:50.189" end="1:50.807">気</span><span begin="1:50.807" end="1:51.328">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">能将心意传达给你的勇气</span></p><p begin="1:51.552" end="1:54.726" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:51.552" end="1:52.155">君</span><span begin="1:52.155" end="1:52.386">を</span><span begin="1:52.386" end="1:52.568">見</span><span begin="1:52.568" end="1:52.943">る</span><span begin="1:52.943" end="1:53.120">と</span><span begin="1:53.120" end="1:53.588">消</span><span begin="1:53.588" end="1:53.751">え</span><span begin="1:53.751" end="1:54.360">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可每次看到你 它就消失不见</span></p><p begin="1:54.726" end="2:00.920" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:54.726" end="1:55.289">一</span><span begin="1:55.289" end="1:55.474">歩</span><span begin="1:55.474" end="1:55.687">も</span><span begin="1:55.687" end="1:56.247">足</span><span begin="1:56.247" end="1:57.347">を</span><span begin="1:57.447" end="1:57.834">踏</span><span begin="1:57.834" end="1:58.031">み</span><span begin="1:58.031" end="1:58.324">出</span><span begin="1:58.324" end="1:58.598">せ</span><span begin="1:58.598" end="2:00.821">な</span><span begin="2:00.821" end="2:00.920">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">靠近你一步都做不到</span></p><p begin="2:01.116" end="2:04.411" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:01.116" end="2:01.452">何</span><span begin="2:01.452" end="2:01.731">度</span><span begin="2:01.731" end="2:02.216">も</span><span begin="2:02.216" end="2:02.489">想</span><span begin="2:02.489" end="2:02.804">像</span><span begin="2:02.804" end="2:03.081">し</span><span begin="2:03.081" end="2:03.255">て</span><span begin="2:03.255" end="2:04.200">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我曾无数次幻想过</span></p><p begin="2:04.411" end="2:07.320" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:04.411" end="2:04.838">君</span><span begin="2:04.838" end="2:04.969">と</span><span begin="2:04.969" end="2:05.236">過</span><span begin="2:05.236" end="2:05.341">ご</span><span begin="2:05.341" end="2:05.574">す</span><span begin="2:05.574" end="2:06.205">日</span><span begin="2:06.205" end="2:06.391">々</span><span begin="2:06.391" end="2:07.320">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们在一起的点点滴滴</span></p><p begin="2:07.598" end="2:10.086" itunes:key="L29" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:07.598" end="2:07.926">夢</span><span begin="2:07.926" end="2:08.163">か</span><span begin="2:08.163" end="2:08.442">ら</span><span begin="2:08.442" end="2:08.751">覚</span><span begin="2:08.751" end="2:09.091">め</span><span begin="2:09.091" end="2:09.341">て</span><span begin="2:09.341" end="2:09.836">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可当梦醒的时候</span></p><p begin="2:10.086" end="2:16.381" itunes:key="L30" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:10.086" end="2:10.863">君</span><span begin="2:10.863" end="2:11.255">が</span><span begin="2:11.255" end="2:12.037">遠</span><span begin="2:12.037" end="2:12.446">く</span><span begin="2:12.446" end="2:12.639">な</span><span begin="2:12.639" end="2:12.832">っ</span><span begin="2:12.832" end="2:13.469">て</span><span begin="2:13.469" end="2:14.010">し</span><span begin="2:14.010" end="2:14.215">ま</span><span begin="2:14.215" end="2:16.381">う</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">你已经快要离我远去</span></p><p begin="2:16.689" end="2:18.664" itunes:key="L31" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:16.689" end="2:16.912">き</span><span begin="2:16.912" end="2:17.134">っ</span><span begin="2:17.134" end="2:17.499">と</span> <span begin="2:17.499" end="2:17.924">忘</span><span begin="2:17.924" end="2:18.261">れ</span><span begin="2:18.261" end="2:18.525">な</span><span begin="2:18.525" end="2:18.664">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我永远不会忘记</span></p><p begin="2:18.664" end="2:22.880" itunes:key="L32" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:18.664" end="2:18.882">こ</span><span begin="2:18.882" end="2:19.217">の</span><span begin="2:19.217" end="2:19.835">胸</span><span begin="2:19.835" end="2:20.111">の</span><span begin="2:20.111" end="2:21.012">切</span><span begin="2:21.012" end="2:21.285">な</span><span begin="2:21.285" end="2:21.987">さ</span><span begin="2:21.987" end="2:22.880">を</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这份心中的难过与酸涩</span></p><p begin="2:23.323" end="2:26.645" itunes:key="L33" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:23.323" end="2:23.721">君</span><span begin="2:23.721" end="2:24.092">に</span><span begin="2:24.092" end="2:24.538">伝</span><span begin="2:24.538" end="2:24.729">え</span><span begin="2:24.729" end="2:25.161">ら</span><span begin="2:25.161" end="2:25.496">れ</span><span begin="2:25.496" end="2:25.682">な</span><span begin="2:25.682" end="2:25.943">か</span><span begin="2:25.943" end="2:26.089">っ</span><span begin="2:26.286" end="2:26.516">た</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">始终未能传达的</span></p><p begin="2:26.645" end="2:29.166" itunes:key="L34" ttm:agent="v2"><span begin="2:26.645" end="2:26.973">&quot;大</span><span begin="2:26.973" end="2:27.220">好</span><span begin="2:27.220" end="2:27.459">き&quot;</span><span begin="2:27.459" end="2:27.680">と</span><span begin="2:27.680" end="2:27.863">い</span><span begin="2:27.863" end="2:28.036">う</span><span begin="2:28.036" end="2:28.617">言</span><span begin="2:28.617" end="2:29.166">葉</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那句“最喜欢你”</span></p><p begin="2:29.166" end="2:31.004" itunes:key="L35" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:29.166" end="2:29.430">今</span><span begin="2:29.430" end="2:29.602">日</span><span begin="2:29.602" end="2:29.900">が</span> <span begin="2:29.900" end="2:30.335">最</span><span begin="2:30.335" end="2:30.514">後</span><span begin="2:30.514" end="2:30.736">だ</span><span begin="2:30.736" end="2:31.004">と</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">如果知道今天是最后一刻</span></p><p begin="2:31.004" end="2:35.080" itunes:key="L36" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:31.004" end="2:31.225">知</span><span begin="2:31.225" end="2:31.352">っ</span><span begin="2:31.352" end="2:31.679">て</span><span begin="2:31.679" end="2:31.893">い</span><span begin="2:31.893" end="2:32.122">た</span><span begin="2:32.122" end="2:32.334">ら</span> <span begin="2:32.334" end="2:32.674">言</span><span begin="2:32.674" end="2:33.095">え</span><span begin="2:33.095" end="2:33.858">た</span><span begin="2:33.858" end="2:34.463">か</span><span begin="2:34.463" end="2:35.080">な</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">是不是就能说出口了呢</span></p><p begin="2:35.206" end="2:38.264" itunes:key="L37" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:35.206" end="2:35.585">遠</span><span begin="2:35.585" end="2:35.801">く</span><span begin="2:35.801" end="2:36.012">な</span><span begin="2:36.012" end="2:36.142">る</span> <span begin="2:36.142" end="2:36.597">君</span><span begin="2:36.597" end="2:36.776">の</span><span begin="2:36.776" end="2:37.137">背</span><span begin="2:37.137" end="2:38.054">中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">渐行渐远的 你的背影</span></p><p begin="2:38.264" end="2:40.935" itunes:key="L38" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:38.264" end="2:38.513">「さ</span><span begin="2:38.513" end="2:38.648">よ</span><span begin="2:38.648" end="2:38.764">う</span><span begin="2:38.764" end="2:38.945">な</span><span begin="2:38.945" end="2:39.145">ら」</span><span begin="2:39.145" end="2:39.335">と</span> <span begin="2:39.335" end="2:39.500">手</span><span begin="2:39.500" end="2:39.720">を</span><span begin="2:39.720" end="2:39.914">振</span><span begin="2:39.914" end="2:40.935">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">挥着手 说着“再见”</span></p><p begin="2:41.069" end="2:45.562" itunes:key="L39" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:41.069" end="2:41.661">永</span><span begin="2:41.661" end="2:42.258">遠</span><span begin="2:42.258" end="2:45.562">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">永别了</span></p></div></body></tt>